Noël Ngiama Makanda kɛna kɛna Kɔŋgoo ɛjaɖɛ taa hendu teyu, tu-luɖu nɛ mʊsɩ laɖʊ sɔsɔ nɔɔyʊ.Palʊla-ɩ saŋgayɩŋ fenaɣ kɩyakʊ 25 wiye pɩnaɣ 1965 kɛ Kikwit ɖoŋgiye taa. Afrika taa lɛ, ɛkɛna hendu teyu weyi e-hendu teu kɛdɩna paa-anɩ yɔ. Paatɛma-ɩ sɩm se ɛkɛna hendu teyaa ŋgbɛyɛ nɖɩ payaɣ-ɖɩ se Wenge Mussika yɔ pa-taa sɔdʊʊ nakʊyʊ. Pɛ-ŋgbɛyɛ-ɖɩ nɖɩ ɖɩ-yɔɔ kɛ Ndombolo lɩwa. Ndombolo ŋgʊ kɩkɛna Koŋgoo ɛjaɖɛ taa amʊsa wena aciida Afrika ɛjɛyɛ nɛ Ka-samaɣ ŋga kɛwɛna ajɛyɛ lɛɛna taa pɩnzɩ 1990 taa yɔ. 
