Ɛnɛ Mpiana pɛkpɛndaa nɛ palɩzɩ tataɣ nakɛyɩ nɛ payaa-kɛ se Mulolo nɛ Kin É Bougé pɩtasɩna Kala-Yi-Boeing. Ŋgbɛ anɛ pʊkɔma pɩtalʊ saŋgayɩŋ fenaɣ kɩyakʊ lʊbɛ wiye pɩnaɣ 1997 lɛ, ɖɩyɔkɩ, mbʊ pʊ-yɔɔ yɔ, ɖama kɩɩnɩnaʊ kaa wɛ Werra nɛ JB Mpiana pɛ-hɛkɩŋ taa. Pɩla mbʊ lɛ, pɛ-ŋgbɛyɛ nɖɩ lɛ ɖɩcɩɩ tɔm nabʊlɛ taa: kacalaɣ hɔɔlʊʊ lɛ, Wenge Musica Maison Mère nɛ Werrason, Didier Masela, Adolphe Dominguez, Christian Mabanga, Japonais Maladi, Ali Mbonda nɛ Ferré Gola; nabʊlɛ taa lɛ, Wenge BCBG Les Anges Adorables nɛ JB Mpiana, Alain Prince Makaba nɛ Blaise Bula nɛ pʊsɔzɩna kɩbɩma lɛlaa.
